Commentary: This implies that he had been upon the Way since many aeons
  before the present world cycle began -- an allusion to the eternity in
  which we all share by reason of our identity with the One Mind
  (note by editor of text).
By: Huang Po
Format: verse
---
\‘How long has Your Reverence been following the Way?’
‘Since before the era of Bhisma Râja.’
